            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-6755942b06d92ad7-f09fcd twpub-6755942b06d92ad7-6b4cd0\"><h4 style=\"\">Section 3.  Information about the Project Gutenberg Literary Archive\nFoundation</h4></div>"
