            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/6755942b06d92ad7/text/000000705",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-6755942b06d92ad7-f09fcd twpub-6755942b06d92ad7-6b4cd0\"><p>For additional contact information:<br>\n\n     Dr. Gregory B. Newby<br>\n\n     Chief Executive and Director<br>\n\n     gbnewby@pglaf.org<br>\n</p></div>"
