            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/6755942b06d92ad7/text/000000706",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-6755942b06d92ad7-f09fcd twpub-6755942b06d92ad7-6b4cd0\"><h4 style=\"\">Section 4.  Information about Donations to the Project Gutenberg\nLiterary Archive Foundation</h4></div>"
