            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/6755942b06d92ad7/text/000000714",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-6755942b06d92ad7-f09fcd twpub-6755942b06d92ad7-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">Project Gutenberg-tm eBooks are often created from several printed\neditions, all of which are confirmed as Public Domain in the U.S.\nunless a copyright notice is included.  Thus, we do not necessarily\nkeep eBooks in compliance with any particular paper edition.</p></div>"
        },
